data.meta_description: Mishti is an bengali film actress Born: 21 December 1992 (age 28 years), West Bengal, India Indrani Chakraborty, known by her mononymous stage name Mishti, is an Indian film actress. She made her Bollywood debut with Subhash Ghai's film Kaanchi: The Unbreakable, She is an actress, known for Kaanchi Dheerga Ayushman Bhava (TBA) Sarabha (2018) Semma Botha Aagathey (2018) Adam Joan (2017) Bruhaspati (2018) Babu Baga Busy (2017) Begum Jaan (2017) Kaanchi (2014)
